Class TripService

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.powdr.service.TripService
  • @Service
public class TripService
extends java.lang.Object
    A Service class for the Trip entity that participates in dependency injection, and performs more detailed methods for obtaining information for the TripController and TripRepository.
